This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game_class "Game class") type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Get / Set the current leader.

Usage
-----

void setLeader( entity leader )

Parameters
----------

-   tba

Examples
--------

    // sets the player as leader for the npc
    $npc_1.setLeader( $player1 );

Notes
-----

Setting the leader to $null\_entity will clear it.

